🌾 FarmSync - Crop & Expense Management System
📌 Overview

FarmSync is a full-stack web application designed to help farmers and agricultural managers efficiently track crops, manage expenses, and monitor farm activities.

It provides a simple dashboard to view insights, manage records, and improve decision-making.


🚀 Features
🌱 Crop Management (Add, View, Update crops)
💰 Expense Tracking
📊 Dashboard with analytics & charts
📅 Activity Monitoring
🔐 User Authentication (Login/Register)
📈 Reports generation
🧾 Recent activities tracking


🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend
React.js
Tailwind CSS
Recharts (for charts)
Backend
Java (Spring Boot)
REST APIs
Maven
Database
